{"tid":1091044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全校都看她的美胸裸照　女師不滿被解雇提9千萬賠償","createTime":"2019-04-04T01:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T06:12:33.000Z","uid":72009,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"faacc14fea993a1fee712d57e67329887d996dee","tid":1091044,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:10:28.000Z","msg":"美國紐約一名25歲女老師米蘭達(Lauren Miranda)，在2016年拍了一張美胸裸照，私傳給她的男友，但這張裸照之後卻被一名學校學生「獨家取得」，導致全校許多同學都看過這張裸照。米蘭達因此被學校解雇，但米蘭達認為這件事錯不在她，認為學校處理不公，昨日和律師一起召開記者會，正式對學校提告，並求償300萬美元(約新台幣9千萬元)。<br />\n<br />\n據《美國今日報》報導，米蘭達和男友同在貝爾波特中學(Bellport Middle School)教書，米蘭達是一位數學老師，平時教學表現優異。她在2016年於家中臥室，拍了一張美胸裸照送給男友，但最後卻流入學校。米蘭達強調，這張照片當時只傳給她的男友，她不知為何最後會被私給一名學生，然後裸照被流傳開來。<br />\n<br />\n校方最後以「行為不檢、榜樣不佳」為由，將米蘭達開除，但米蘭達相當不滿，她指出這張照片並沒有特意傳給學生，因此沒有違反學校任何紀錄規定。再者，她認為校方有性別歧視，她說：「這是我的胸部，是我身體的一部分，我不認為我這樣子做有什麼不對。」律師雷伊(John Ray)也表示，如果今天是男老師拍上空照，就不會覺得有任何問題，「這起事件只是因為發生在一個女人身上，然後她就被開除了」，因此米蘭達向校方求償300萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n米蘭達也直呼，自己從18歲起就奉獻給這間學校，但現在只是因為一個無心事件，就這樣被開除，「我的職業、名譽都毀了，已經帶給我難以抹滅的恥辱」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190404/1545142/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190404%2F1545142%2F&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=1fb5373f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190404%2F1545142%2F&h=37345bb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190404/1545142/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190404/640_788a8870c790718a4f74032282cd9bf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190404%2F640_788a8870c790718a4f74032282cd9bf6.jpg&h=98f6955b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190404/640_22120c7d87128f196cc01de8e451027b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190404%2F640_22120c7d87128f196cc01de8e451027b.jpg&h=5c87621c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定PINK LIN"},{"pid":"30ed62e462dcce1f90671d303c896d1ac5f9d733","tid":1091044,"uid":205377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2340610ebe25c659490237c066771c1d8942de","tid":1091044,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:15:58.000Z","msg":"我有講過"},{"pid":"227702a2557ec621ebc5ab233fa7c8964d3421a3","tid":1091044,"uid":68732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:16:59.000Z","msg":"騎兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4633a0a20eb9abaddb4b2d4593066249f98846","tid":1091044,"uid":172507,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38499f49a2e930b2167a7e4b92d5ffa862f1233a","tid":1091044,"uid":4180,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但這張裸照之後卻被一名學校學生「獨家取得」，導致全校許多同學都看過這張裸照。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個o靚仔認真唔話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw可唔可以分享埋黎連登"},{"pid":"a72c9cffa573cf8c1af1b75840b51f2385c9cdc9","tid":1091044,"uid":146535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:24:17.000Z","msg":"係咪分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cafd6550e797e7e22857564337ea4790b9f8dab","tid":1091044,"uid":24877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc